Iheme Faith Uloma (amụrụ na 23 Julaị [mgbe?]) nke a maara nke ọma dị ka Ifu Ennada bụ onye Naijirịa na-eme ihe nkiri na onye na-emepụta ejiji na onye bụbu onye BBNaija. Ọ bụkwa onye na-eme ihe nkiri, nke a maara maka mmeri AMAA maka Best Young and Promising Actor na ihe nkiri O-Town
A mụrụ Ennada na Abia State, Naijirịa mana a zụlitere ya na Lagos
Ọ gụrụ sayensị kọmputa na Mahadum Olabisi Onabanjo ebe ọ nwetara BSc ya

Ọ malitere ọrụ ihe nkiri ya na 2019 na 2016, a họpụtara ya maka Best Young / Promomising Actor na ihe nkiri O-Town na AMAA awards 2016. N'ajụjụ ọnụ nke afọ 2018, ọ kpughere na a wakporo ya n'afọ 2016.
N'afọ 2018, o sonyere na Big Brother Naija game show.
